[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":270},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F01\u002F01\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F01\u002F01\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F01\u002F01\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F01\u002F01\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan\u002F":245,"related:\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F01\u002F01\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan\u002F":254},"\u002Fother\u002F20220101\u002F2179285582\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":224,"date":225,"description":226,"extension":227,"lang":228,"meta":229,"navigation":230,"path":231,"readingMinutes":232,"seo":233,"standalone":234,"stem":235,"tags":236,"tldr":242,"updated":242,"url":243,"__hash__":244},"content\u002Fen\u002FMisc\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan.md","Receiving Google AdSense Wire-Transfer Payouts (Richart \u002F Taiwan Example)","9285582172",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":216},"minimark",[11,16,20,28,32,35,38,45,48,54,57,79,85,88,94,97,112,118,121,127,133,136,142,145,151,155,162,168,171,177,180,186,192,195,201,204,208],[12,13,15],"h2",{"id":14},"intro","Intro",[17,18,19],"p",{},"My AdSense balance finally hit the payout threshold, so I'm writing down how I set up wire transfer using Richart (Taishin International Bank, Taiwan).",[21,22,25],"callout",{"title":23,"type":24},"Note","note",[17,26,27],{},"This walkthrough uses Richart as the example, since that's what I use in Taiwan. The AdSense-side fields and process are universal across countries — only the bank specifics differ. The minimum payout threshold for wire transfer is $100 USD globally.",[12,29,31],{"id":30},"adsense-payout-setup","AdSense payout setup",[17,33,34],{},"Once your blog hits the payout minimum (~$100 USD), you can claim. Walking through wire transfer via Richart.",[17,36,37],{},"Open Google AdSense → Payments → \"Add payment method\":",[17,39,40],{},[41,42],"img",{"alt":43,"src":44},"Add payment method","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96_2021-12-30_17_00_06.png",[17,46,47],{},"Pick \"Add wire transfer details\":",[17,49,50],{},[41,51],{"alt":52,"src":53},"Add wire transfer details","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-01-01%2000.45.11.png",[17,55,56],{},"The form needs:",[58,59,60,64,67,70,73,76],"ul",{},[61,62,63],"li",{},"Beneficiary ID",[61,65,66],{},"Bank account name",[61,68,69],{},"Bank name",[61,71,72],{},"SWIFT BIC",[61,74,75],{},"Account number",[61,77,78],{},"Confirm account number",[17,80,81],{},[41,82],{"alt":83,"src":84},"Wire fields","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96%202022-01-01%2000.51.11.png",[17,86,87],{},"For Richart users — open the Richart mobile app → Foreign Exchange → \"See more\":",[17,89,90],{},[41,91],{"alt":92,"src":93},"Foreign exchange","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201010053.png",[17,95,96],{},"You'll see your foreign-currency account details:",[58,98,99,102,104,106,109],{},[61,100,101],{},"English account name",[61,103,75],{},[61,105,69],{},[61,107,108],{},"Branch",[61,110,111],{},"International wire code (SWIFT\u002FBIC)",[17,113,114],{},[41,115],{"alt":116,"src":117},"Account details","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201010057.png",[17,119,120],{},"Note these down and head back to the AdSense wire form. Fill it in:",[17,122,123],{},[124,125,126],"strong",{},"PS — Bank account name = your English name. The screenshot shows the bank name as placeholder for demo purposes.",[17,128,129],{},[41,130],{"alt":131,"src":132},"Filled form","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201010059.png",[17,134,135],{},"Save. Once your balance hits the $100 threshold, AdSense automatically wires the payout to that account:",[17,137,138],{},[41,139],{"alt":140,"src":141},"Auto payout","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201010101.png",[17,143,144],{},"You'll get a notification each payout cycle:",[17,146,147],{},[41,148],{"alt":149,"src":150},"Payout notice","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201010102.png",[12,152,154],{"id":153},"after-the-wire-arrives-richart-specific","After the wire arrives (Richart-specific)",[17,156,157,158,161],{},"About 5 days later, the wire arrives in Richart. Heads up — Richart requires you to manually ",[124,159,160],{},"claim"," the incoming wire. Open Richart → Foreign Exchange and you'll see a \"pending receipt\" status:",[17,163,164],{},[41,165],{"alt":166,"src":167},"Pending receipt","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201182030.png",[17,169,170],{},"Tap in to see the Google payout:",[17,172,173],{},[41,174],{"alt":175,"src":176},"Google payout","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201182037.png",[17,178,179],{},"Scroll down → pick the transaction purpose → confirm:",[17,181,182],{},[41,183],{"alt":184,"src":185},"Receive","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201082039.png",[17,187,188],{},[41,189],{"alt":190,"src":191},"Received","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201182042.png",[17,193,194],{},"Now the funds show up in your USD foreign-exchange account:",[17,196,197],{},[41,198],{"alt":199,"src":200},"USD account","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fother\u002F202201182043.png",[17,202,203],{},"That's the actual money in hand.",[12,205,207],{"id":206},"heads-up","Heads up",[58,209,210,213],{},[61,211,212],{},"Use a foreign-currency account (USD-capable). AdSense pays in USD.",[61,214,215],{},"Claim incoming wires within 5 days. After that, Richart auto-returns the wire to AdSense.",{"title":217,"searchDepth":218,"depth":218,"links":219},"",2,[220,221,222,223],{"id":14,"depth":218,"text":15},{"id":30,"depth":218,"text":31},{"id":153,"depth":218,"text":154},{"id":206,"depth":218,"text":207},"Misc","2022-01-01 01:02:02","Five-minute walkthrough of setting up Google AdSense wire-transfer payouts. The bank used here is Richart (Taishin International Bank, Taiwan) — the specifics are Taiwan-flavored, but the general flow (find your foreign-currency account details, fill in AdSense's wire details form, wait for the $100 threshold, claim the incoming wire) applies to AdSense payouts in any country.","md","en",{},true,"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan","2",{"title":6,"description":226},false,"en\u002FMisc\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan",[237,238,239,240,241],"Richart","Taishin Bank","Google AdSense Payout","Google AdSense","Wire Transfer",null,"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F01\u002F01\u002Freceive-google-adsense-wire-transfer-payouts-richart-taiwan\u002F","bw0Q1bfMR-gPKqlrMnpE9R7TmYYPCuEE5KuX-8EIHv8",{"newer":246,"older":250},{"url":247,"title":248,"date":249},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2022\u002F01\u002F04\u002Fcommon-http-status-codes-2xx-4xx-5xx\u002F","Common HTTP Status Codes — 2xx, 4xx, 5xx Explained","2022-01-04 10:04:06",{"url":251,"title":252,"date":253},"\u002Fen\u002Fnuxt\u002F2021\u002F12\u002F26\u002Fnuxt-2x-handbook-06-head-config\u002F","Nuxt.js 2.x Hands-On Handbook (6) — Head Configuration","2021-12-26 16:53:22",[255,260,265],{"url":256,"title":257,"date":258,"readingMinutes":259},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2026\u002F07\u002F10\u002F100-day-body-recomposition-experiment\u002F","My 100-Day Body Recomposition Experiment, as a Software Engineer","2026-07-10 09:53:56","23",{"url":261,"title":262,"date":263,"readingMinutes":264},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2026\u002F06\u002F23\u002Fmac-stats-menu-bar-system-monitor\u002F","Stats — The Free Open-Source macOS Menu Bar System Monitor I Use Every Day (CPU, GPU, Temperature, Network)","2026-06-23 10:00:00","5",{"url":266,"title":267,"date":268,"readingMinutes":269},"\u002Fen\u002Fmisc\u002F2026\u002F05\u002F26\u002Fhow-much-does-a-blog-really-earn-with-google-adsense\u002F","Can a Blog Really Make Tens of Thousands of Dollars a Month? Real Google AdSense Numbers, Explained","2026-05-26 21:00:00","6",1784087334327]